Now, I'm going to get to
the second mystery, which

00:26:24.690 --> 00:26:25.670
Einstein--

00:26:25.670 --> 00:26:27.660
Einstein was such
a brilliant man.

00:26:27.660 --> 00:26:32.280
He always brought up new
extraordinary concepts.

00:26:32.280 --> 00:26:36.180
And this is spooky
action at a distance.

